# AiDoc.WebNew — Self-Contained RAG Handler

All code required to run this application lives inside `src\AiDoc.WebNew`. It is independent and self-contained as a RAG management portal.

## Only Build Dependency

- `DedgeAuth.Client` → for authentication (project reference to `C:\opt\src\DedgeAuth`)

## No Dependency On Any Other AiDoc Subfolder

This project has no build or source dependency on:
- `src\AiDoc.Web` — old project, replaced by this one
- `src\AiDoc.Pwsh.Server`
- `src\AiDoc.Pwsh.Client`
- `src\AiDoc.Pwsh.Dev`
- `AiDoc.Python`
- `docs`, `scripts`, `_unsorted`

## Deployment

The `Build-And-Publish.ps1` in this folder is the only script needed to build and publish this project.
